        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry trends come and go, but earrings remain timeless. From adding grace to your workwear to being the centerpiece of your evening look, earrings define how you express your style. Yet, with so many varieties - danglers, drops, huggies, hoops, balis and J-balis it’s easy to wonder what truly sets each apart.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, each design is more than just an accessory - it’s an emotion captured in precious metal and ethically crafted stones. Whether you’re shopping online at Lucira’s official site or visiting a Lucira experience store in <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sky-city-borivali-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Mumbai</span></a>, or their newer location on <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/pune-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">JM Road in Pune</span></a>, understanding earring styles will help you make choices that enhance your natural elegance and suit every occasion.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_q6jXJi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Danglers vs. Drops: Movement, Elegance and Statement",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. Danglers vs. Drops: Movement, Elegance and Statement</h2>",
            "custom_id": "danglers",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_C4KUKT": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image with Text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/diamond_image_1.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Danglers and drops are often confused, but the difference lies in their movement and length.</p><ul><li>Drops hang just below the earlobe and typically stay still. They’re designed with simplicity in mind -   think of a single pearl, gemstone, or diamond drop that adds effortless sophistication. They work perfectly for office wear, formal gatherings, and brunches.</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "cut",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "kite-shape-drops-dangle-diamond-earrings",
              "celestia-pear-diamond-drops-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Danglers, however, are designed for movement. They sway gracefully as you walk, creating a fluid shimmer that draws attention. Long danglers with delicate chains or layers are ideal for evening events or festive occasions.</li></ul><p>If you’re pairing earrings with necklaces, explore Lucira’s exquisite<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">collections</span></a> for pieces that blend seamlessly with your preferred earring type - be it minimalist drops or ornate danglers.</p><p>Styling Tip: For round or oval faces, opt for long danglers to elongate your look. For angular or narrow faces, shorter drops add balance and charm.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_edc69T": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. Huggies vs. Hoops: Comfort Meets Confidence",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2. Huggies vs. Hoops: Comfort Meets Confidence</h2>",
            "custom_id": "huggies",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ry4cQt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text ",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/color.jpg",
            "text": "<p>When it comes to versatile elegance, huggies and hoops are timeless favorites. They both share a circular design but differ in fit, size, and overall feel.</p><ul><li>Huggies are small earrings that “hug” your earlobes snugly. Their minimal design makes them ideal for daily wear and layering with multiple piercings. Pair them with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a> to complete an understated, luxurious look that transitions easily from work to dinner.</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "crescent-swirl-diamond-huggies-earrings",
              "round-diamond-hoop-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Hoops, by contrast, are larger circles that can range from thin metallic bands to diamond-studded statements. They symbolize boldness and are perfect for those who love making a confident style statement.</li></ul><p>Styling Tip: Medium-sized hoops add structure to round faces, while larger hoops enhance sharper jawlines. Try pairing your hoops with a sleek bun or ponytail for an effortlessly chic vibe.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Clarity",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Clarity</h2><p>Clarity measures the purity of a diamond. During a diamond’s formation, it’s common for tiny impurities to become trapped either inside the diamond or on its surface.</p>",
            "custom_id": "clarity",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_BiE3eV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Clarity",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Clarity.webp",
            "text": "<p>Clarity characteristics are divided into two types: <em>Inclusions</em> (internal features) and <em>Blemishes</em> (external marks). Even when these are too small to be seen without magnification, they can still affect how light moves through the diamond. As a result, their size, shape, and position play an important role in diamond grading. Importantly, <em>Inclusions</em> do not affect the structural stability of a diamond.</p><p>There are 11 clarity grades, ranging from <em>FL</em> (flawless internally and externally) to <em>I</em> (with significant inclusions and blemishes).</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-20-cts-dewdrop-diamond-ring",
              "0-25-cts-classic-solitaire-diamond-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Make sure to check a diamond’s certificate before you make a purchase, as a diamond with fewer imperfections will come at a higher asking price. Imperfections also give each diamond its own unique character, and to many, these add to its beauty.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Carat",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Carat</h2><p>Carat is a measurement of weight, derived from the word \"carob\"; in ancient times, carob seeds were used as a reference for diamond weight.</p>",
            "custom_id": "carat",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XgNzg9": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Carat",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/carat.jpg",
            "text": "<p>One carat weighs 1/5 of a gram and is divided into 100 points, so a diamond weighing 1.05 ct. is referred to as \"one carat and five points\". Today, precise measurements are taken to the hundredth decimal place to ensure complete accuracy.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-44ct-half-eternity-pave-diamond-band",
              "0-4ct-emerald-round-toi-et-moi-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Diamond prices rise exponentially with carat weight. So, a 2-carat diamond of a given quality is always worth more than two 1-carat diamonds of the same quality. However, the carat weight by itself does not determine a diamond’s value. Two diamonds of equal carat weight may have very different values based on the other factors: all the 4Cs have an influence on each other in diamond grading.</p><h2>Conclusion</h2><p>Lab Grown Diamonds have opened a world of possibilities, offering the same brilliance, strength and beauty as mined diamonds but at a far more accessible price. Grown under conditions that replicate the earth’s natural processes, they share the exact same physical and chemical properties as their mined counterparts, differing only in their origin.</p><p>Like Mined Diamonds, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry's</a> Lab Grown Diamonds are graded by the 4Cs, giving you a trusted framework to understand a diamond's qualities. However, the 4Cs are simply a guide, not a rulebook. No two diamonds are alike, true beauty lies in what you personally connect with and that’s what makes it truly special.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
